<h1>Adoption</h1>
<p>If you're looking to adopt a Husky you should consider all the responsibilites that come with dog ownership and especially the indivial needs of a Husky.</p>

<p> Many people wrongly adopt Huskies because of their cuteness and their kindness and forget to consider their needs. You need to consider the dogs high energy in your lifestyle and their tendency to howl. For these reasons typically apartments are not good are this breed of dog. </p>

<h2> Places to adopt from </h2>
<a href="http://foreverhusky.org/?gclid=CIDZ-IfLuc0CFQ8yaQodICA"> Forever Husky</a> <br/>

<a href="http://ravenshuskyhavenandrescue.org/why-rhhr.html"> Ravens Husky Haven and Rescue </a> <br/>

<a href="http://www.alleysrescuedangels.org/donate/">Alleys Rescued Angels </a> <br/>
<p> or look at your local humane society. </p>
